**Summary of ASX Announcement:**  

- **Announcement Type:** Daily buy-back notification (Appendix 3C)  
- **Buy-back Type:** On-market  
- **Total shares bought back before previous day:** 10,413,955  
- **Shares bought back on previous day (18/6/2025):** 120,000  
- **Total consideration paid:** AUD 55,140 (previous day) | AUD 4,958,370 (cumulative)  
- **Highest/lowest price paid (previous day):** AUD 0.465 (high) | AUD 0.455 (low)  
- **Buy-back period:** 25/3/2025 to 25/3/2026  
- **Target:** Up to 10% of ordinary shares (no fixed minimum/maximum).  
- **Broker:** Morgans Financial Limited  

**Material Impact:**  
- Ongoing liquidity reduction via buy-back (~1.6% of shares outstanding repurchased to date).  
- No shareholder approval required; discretionary execution.
